title: Lust
overview: »A long-form music video which recalls the early shorts of the Cinema of Transgression mixed with the sensibilities of Sun Ra and George Clinton and Kenneth Anger, the images of explicit queer BSDM sex and Satanic ritual between Master Satanas{Uhuru Moor} and Doomsfae{Sha Gaze} filmed in Joshua Tree, California are not for the faint of heart. « {Walter Crasshole}
